data.description: Beautiful Updated home in the wonderful Kentwood Neighborhood. So close to schools that you could walk! Amazing Flat front and back yard. Lots of windows bringing outside light into every room. Ring Security System Large spacious rooms Huge master suite with updated bathroom tile and shower throughtout the house . Smart Plugs Main level living at its best. 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, Large den with fireplace. Kitchen has lots of cabinets, island, breakfast room (TV Stays).  newer Deck with awning, wonderful for grilling & entertaining. Lower level, boasts of bedroom/full bath/ family room leads out to an beautiful patio (TV, patio lights stays), fenced backyard, mature landscaping. Newer Heat Pump! Closets galore and  finished basement that will be great for workout spaces, storage, etc. Award winning Alabaster schools! Move in ready house  Samsung fridge upstairs does not stay and all curtains/drapes don't stay
